Dependencies : clang-3.6 llvm-3.6

http://llvm.org/releases/3.6.0/cfe-3.6.0.src.tar.xz
http://llvm.org/releases/3.6.0/llvm-3.6.0.src.tar.xz

http://llvm.org/docs/GettingStarted.html

After building llvm and clang, LLVM_CONFIG_PATH CLANG_INCLUDE_PATH and CLANG_LIB_PATH
must be updated in the Makefile.